        "description": "<p>You can display product categories and/or subcategories on your archive pages of Woocommerce.</p>\n",
        "installation": "<p>Follow four steps:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Activate the plugin through the &#8216;Plugins&#8217; menu in WordPress</li>\n<li>In Dashboard, go to In-Store Product categories</li>\n<li>Check &#8220;Display Products Categories in Shop Page.&#8221;</li>\n<li>Click &#8220;Save Changes&#8221;</li>\n</ol>\n",
        "changelog": "<h4>1.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>First version.</li>\n</ul>\n",
        "faq": "\n<h4>Installation Instructions</h4>\n<p>\n<p>Follow four steps:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Activate the plugin through the &#8216;Plugins&#8217; menu in WordPress</li>\n<li>In Dashboard, go to In-Store Product categories</li>\n<li>Check &#8220;Display Products Categories in Shop Page.&#8221;</li>\n<li>Click &#8220;Save Changes&#8221;</li>\n</ol>\n</p>\n\n"
    },
